casebody.data:
STATE EX REL. MANGUN
v.
OLIVITO 2018-1495 Supreme Court of Ohio. May 14, 2019

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

Relator has not filed a merit brief, due May 10, 2019, in compliance with the Rules of Practice of the Supreme Court of Ohio and therefore has failed to prosecute this cause with the requisite diligence. Cause dismissed. Respondent's motion to dismiss denied as moot.
